---
title: Brie Cheese, Mushroom and Caramelized Onion Sandwich with French Green Bean and Cashew Salad
description: It’s time to bring your childhood favourite into adulthood. Melty brie and sweet caramelized onions create the ultimate sweet and salty sammie. Crispy french beans and crunchy cashews amp up a simple side salad.
